OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after sex with
OL,4,Cinmate in cell
OL,6,FA prison officer has been jailed for
OL,7,F15 months after having sex with an
OL,8,Finmate in a cell.
OL,10,FLinda De Sousa Abreu, 30, of Fulham,
OL,11,Fsouth-west London, was charged after a
OL,12,Fvideo of the activity was shared on
OL,13,Fsocial media.
OL,15,FA police investigation was launched
OL,16,Fafter officers were made aware of a
OL,17,Fvideo filmed inside HMP Wandsworth in
OL,18,Fsouth London.
