OL,3,CPrison officer jailed after sex with
OL,4,Cinmate in cell
OL,6,FDe Sousa Abreu was arrested and
OL,7,Fpleaded guilty to misconduct in public
OL,8,Foffice, at Isleworth Crown Court, in
OL,9,FJuly last year.
OL,11,FShe appeared at the same court on
OL,12,FMonday, where she was sentenced to 15
OL,13,Fmonths in prison.
OL,15,FThe charge says that De Sousa Abreu
OL,16,F"wilfully and without reasonable
OL,17,Fexcuse or justification misconducted
OL,18,Fyourself in a way which amounted to an
OL,19,Fabuse of the public's trust in the
OL,20,Foffice holder by engaging in a sexual
OL,21,Fact with a prisoner in a prison cell".
