OL,6,FIt happened at Wandsworth between June
OL,7,F26 and 28.
OL,9,FShe was arrested at Heathrow Airport
OL,10,Fand was due to catch a flight to
OL,11,FMadrid, having notified the prison of
OL,12,Fher travel plans.
OL,14,FA Prison Service spokesperson said:
OL,15,F"While the overwhelming majority of
OL,16,FPrison Service staff are hardworking
OL,17,Fand honest, we're catching more of the
OL,18,Fsmall minority who break the rules by
OL,19,Fbolstering our Counter Corruption Unit
OL,20,Fand strengthening our vetting
OL,21,Fprocesses.
